---
import { CONTACT_INFO, getWhatsAppLink } from '../data/config'

const navItems = [
  { name: 'Planes', href: '#planes' },
  { name: 'Cobertura', href: '#cobertura' },
  { name: 'Convenios', href: '#features' },
  { name: 'Contacto', href: '#contacto' }
]
---

<header class="relative w-full min-h-[90vh] flex flex-col overflow-hidden">
  <nav class="absolute top-0 w-full z-50 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-slate-200">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 h-20 flex items-center justify-between">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="bg-blue-700 p-2 rounded-lg">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="w-6 h-6 text-white"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor"
          >
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <span class="text-blue-900 font-black text-xl tracking-tighter leading-none"
            >RESCATES M칄DICOS</span
          >
          <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 font-bold"
            >Contrataci칩n Autorizada Chile</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8">
        {
          navItems.map((item) => (
            <a
              href={item.href}
              class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors"
            >
              {item.name}
            </a>
          ))
        }
        <a
          href={`tel:${CONTACT_INFO.phone}`}
          class="bg-blue-700 text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full text-sm font-bold hover:bg-blue-800 transition-all shadow-lg shadow-blue-200 flex items-center gap-2"
        >
          <span>游</span> Llamar a {CONTACT_INFO.name}
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="relative flex-1 flex items-center pt-20 p-5">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <img
        src="/images/rescate.png"
        alt="Rescate m칠dico nocturno ambulancia"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-900 via-slate-900/70 to-slate-900/30"
      >
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 w-full py-12 md:py-0">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <div
          class="mt-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-blue-600/30 backdrop-blur-md border border-blue-400/30 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6 text-blue-50 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest"
        >
          <span class="flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-green-400 animate-pulse"></span>
          Atenci칩n Inmediata con {CONTACT_INFO.name}
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white leading-tight mb-6">
          Ambulancias de rescate Privado, <br />
          <span class="text-blue-400">en la puerta de tu casa en minutos</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-200 mb-8 max-w-xl leading-relaxed font-medium">
          No contrates a ciegas. Como <strong>Ejecutiva Autorizada</strong>, Contrata HOY PLANES
          <strong class="text-white">de rescate Famila o Empresa</strong>, para que obtengas la
          mejor cobertura en Santiago y Valpara칤so.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 items-start sm:items-center">
          <a
            href={getWhatsAppLink()}
            target="_blank"
            class="w-full sm:w-auto group inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-black text-lg transition-all hover:scale-105 shadow-xl shadow-green-900/30"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="w-7 h-7"
              fill="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                d="M.057 24l1.687-6.163c-1.041-1.804-1.588-3.849-1.588-5.946 0-6.556 5.332-11.888 11.887-11.888 3.174 0 6.16 1.236 8.41 3.484 2.247 2.247 3.487 5.232 3.487 8.406 0 6.555-5.332 11.89-11.888 11.89-1.941 0-3.843-.48-5.544-1.391l-6.451 1.608zm10.635-19.587c-1.159 0-2.236.446-3.034 1.253-.806.808-1.254 1.884-1.254 3.041 0 1.054.39 2.048 1.067 2.871l.19.233-.677 2.469 2.53-.662.223.132c.767.457 1.648.699 2.557.699 1.159 0 2.246-.449 3.051-1.255.807-.809 1.253-1.885 1.253-3.042 0-2.366-1.922-4.29-4.288-4.29z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
            Cotizar Plan con {CONTACT_INFO.name}
          </a>

          <a
            href="#planes"
            class="w-full sm:w-auto inline-flex justify-center bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm text-white border border-white/30 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg transition-all"
          >
            Ver Precios
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-white italic">0,59 UF</div>
            <div
              class="text-[10px] leading-tight uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 font-bold"
            >
              Desde el plan <br /> m치s b치sico
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-white italic">24/7</div>
            <div
              class="text-[10px] leading-tight uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 font-bold"
            >
              Respuesta <br /> inmediata
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-blue-400 italic">100%</div>
            <div
              class="text-[10px] leading-tight uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 font-bold"
            >
              Gesti칩n <br /> Digital
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
